<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
	
<img src="http://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/images/logo.gif"/><br/><br/>

<p>
Personal message from:
<% if @cdata['message'].remote_sender -%>
    <a href="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/people/remote/<%= @cdata['message'].remote_sender.id %>/profile?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>"><%= @cdata['message'].remote_sender.name %> (<%= @cdata['message'].remote_sender.account %>)</a>
<% elsif @cdata['message'].sender -%>
    <a href="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/participant/<%= @message.from_participant_id %>/profile?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>"><%= @cdata['message'].sender.name %></a>
<% else -%>
    ???
<% end -%>
</p>

<div>
<%=raw @message %>
</div>

<hr/>

Manage your contacts in the <a href="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/me/friends?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>">Friends</a> Area<img src="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/pixel/<%= @cdata['message'].id.to_i if @cdata['message'] %>.gif" width="0" height="0" border="0" style="display:none">. To block emails from the Voices of Humanity social media, <a href="https://<%= BASEDOMAIN %>/optout?auth_token=<%= @cdata['recipient'].authentication_token %>">click here</a>.

</body>
</html>